<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer12981843754159999082">The Septembers of Shiraz is Dalia Sofer&apos;s first novel. She was born in 1972 in Tehran, Iran and fled at the age of ten to the United States with her family. She received her MFA in Fiction from Sarah Lawrence College in 2002 and has been a resident at Yaddo. She currently resides in New York City. <br/></span>
  <span id="freeText12981843754159999082" style="display:none">The Septembers of Shiraz is Dalia Sofer's first novel. She was born in 1972 in Tehran, Iran and fled at the age of ten to the United States with her family. She received her MFA in Fiction from Sarah Lawrence College in 2002 and has been a resident at Yaddo. She currently resides in New York City. <br /></span>
